%F A090672 a(n) = (n+3)! * Sum_{k=1..n} (k+1)!/(k+3)!, with offset 0. - _Gary Detlefs_, Aug 05 2010
%F A090672 E.g.f.: (x^3 - 3*x^2)/(3*(x-1)^3). - _Geoffrey Critzer_, Mar 04 2013
